thor-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%99-thu-u%E1%BB%95ng-B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ch%C3%A2u-th%E1%BB%A7-tr%C3%A1t-su%E1%BA%A5t-nh%C4%A9-khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%C3%BD-c%E1%BA%ADn-tr%C3%ACnh-T%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1/poem-OBlyRxjh5TCqFh5dGFYn3g">Mộ thu uổng Bùi Đạo Châu thủ trát, suất nhĩ khiển hứng, ký cận trình Tô Hoán thị ngự - 暮秋枉裴道州手札，率爾遣興，寄近呈蘇渙侍御</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Phu-Ti%C3%AAn/Ng%C3%A3-ngu/poem-VVQ2-xVAYRKT-rFZSoriGg">Ngã ngu - 我愚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Phu-Ti%C3%AAn/author-0-fToxuPehWo6bV9a9n8ew">Phan Phu Tiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-051/poem-1tip3669zaTHdgXEPv7hPg">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 051 - 山居百詠其五十一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Thanh-b%C3%ACnh-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-YGXtqjJz9I3lyd9U9uryRw">Thanh bình điệu kỳ 2 - 清平調其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%E1%BB%87p-giang/poem-csh8ujkV1cSEGuoKbE1Ufg">Thiệp giang - 涉江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
